ged to the current callsign of '''KBMN-LD'' on March 11, 2013.<ref>http://www.fccinfo.com/CMDProEngine.php?sCurrentService=TV&tabSearchType=Appl&sAppIDNumber=188068</ref>\n\n==Digital channels==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! [[Digital subchannel#United States|Channel]]\n! [[Display resolution|Video]]\n! [[Aspect ratio (image)|Aspect]]\n! [[Program and System Information Protocol#What PSIP does|PSIP Short \nName]]\n! Programming<ref name=dtv/>\n|-\n| 40.1 \n| rowspan=4|[[480i]] \n| rowspan=4|[[4:3]] \n| rowspan=4| KBMN-LD\n| [[3ABN]] \n|- \n| 40.2 \n| Infomercials \n|- \n| 40.3 \n| Infomercials \n|- \n| 40.4\n| [[Cheddar (TV channel)|Cheddar]]\n|}\n\n==References== \n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{TVQ|KBMN-LD}}\n\n{{Houston TV}}\n{{DTV America}}\n\n[[Category:Digital low-power stations]]\n[[Category:DTV America]]\n[[Category:Television stations in Texas]]\n[[Category:Television channels and stations established in 2019]]\n[[Category:2019 establishments in Texas]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox broadcast\n| call_letters             = KBMN-LD \n| city                     = Houston, Texas\n| station_logo             =  \n| station_branding         =  \n| station_slogan           =  \n| digital                  = 9 ([[very high frequency|VHF]])\n| virtual                  = 40 ([[Program and System Information Protocol|PSIP]]) \n| subchannels              = [[#Digital channels|(see below)]]\n| other_chs                = \n| affiliations             = [[#Digital channels|(see below)]] \n| location                 = [[Houston, Texas]]\n| country                  = [[United States]]\n| owner                    = [[HC2 Holdings]]\n| licensee                 = [[DTV America]] Corporation\n| founded                  = 2019\n| airdate                  = {{start date and age|2019|11|12|p=y}}  \n| callsign_meaning         =   \n| sister_stations          = \n| former_callsigns         = K40NM-D (2012-2013)\n| former_affiliations      =  \n| former_channel_numbers   = \n| effe